171 A.3d 1261 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. SAINT H. MERILAN A/K/A, SAINT HILAIRE MERILAN, SAINT H. MERIALN, SAINT MERILAN, JASON WILLIAMS, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-217 Sept. Tern 2017

079388 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002826-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
